{"tid":504562,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北海道30年內 恐爆9級強震","createTime":"2017-12-20T07:00:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-20T07:59:16.000Z","uid":10958,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c3b1fa93f6dc34c6b0c0d4c0bd94601762c67c8c","tid":504562,"uid":10958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T07:00:56.000Z","msg":"<strong>北海道30年內 恐爆9級強震</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/1970000/1974249/20JIA004__20171220_L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1970000%2F1974249%2F20JIA004__20171220_L.jpg&h=d728e45b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">日本2011年大地震釀成海嘯。（資料圖片）</span><br />\n<br />\n日本政府估算北海道海域於未來30年內，有40%機會發生9級大地震，呼籲盡快作預防對策。<br />\n<br />\n官方地震調查委員會指北海道東部近海，30年內發生8.8級以上的強震機率達40%，屆時所造成傷害將不亞於311大地震。委員會分析過去海嘯將海底砂土捲上陸地形成的沉積物，指北海道海域的相關板塊每隔340年至380年就會發生一次強震，距離上次地震已約400年，因此快將發生強震的可能性提高。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/1974249/%E5%8C%97%E6%B5%B7%E9%81%9330%E5%B9%B4%E5%85%A7%20%E6%81%90%E7%88%869%E7%B4%9A%E5%BC%B7%E9%9C%87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fskypost.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F1974249%2F%25E5%258C%2597%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E9%2581%259330%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%2585%25A7%2520%25E6%2581%2590%25E7%2588%25869%25E7%25B4%259A%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E9%259C%2587&d=Xg0MilhLFswsUtwzR4mAVDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=9f0964af\" target=\"_blank\">https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/1974249/%E5%8C%97%E6%B5%B7%E9%81%9330%E5%B9%B4%E5%85%A7%20%E6%81%90%E7%88%869%E7%B4%9A%E5%BC%B7%E9%9C%87</a>"},{"pid":"b0f7f0651f6f67037e8c79dab9bc9ba01200b754","tid":504562,"uid":145247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T07:29:50.000Z","msg":"日本正辣殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a8457e01150aa9f368e916a92d21a9ba3df9aea","tid":504562,"uid":2155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T07:52:28.000Z","msg":"30 年內<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f6328c43869033b3440615fb890a9523def3c47","tid":504562,"uid":41974,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T07:53:46.000Z","msg":"一萬年內人類可能絕種"},{"pid":"16293cc1b42778f29860c18dbcf02434150cd017","tid":504562,"uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T07:55:29.000Z","msg":"30年內，恐董建華會死"},{"pid":"949403f8b7e2136f13b653f0c63936e2fa237b0a","tid":504562,"uid":61257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T07:59:16.000Z","msg":"30年光陰係地球上真係好微少時間<br />\n<br />\n人就唔同 十年幾翻生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}